{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/vigramsdk\/useresetvidoc"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"","type":"heading","anchor":""},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The viDoc reset procedure returns the settings to factory defaults."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note:"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" Perform this procedure only if absolutely necessary."}]},{"style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The reset procedure takes approximately 1 minute."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"At the beginning of the process, all messages are interrupted."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Disconnection from all satellites occurs."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"After the viDoc is reset, sending messages resumes."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You must wait to receive the full NMEA GGA message."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside","name":"Note"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To track the reset process, you need to use publisher"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["private var cancellables = Set<AnyCancellable>()","","peripheral.viDocResetState","    .sink(receiveCompletion: { completion in","        switch completion {","        case .finished:","            break \/\/ normal completion","        case .failure(let error):","            \/\/ do something with error","        }","    }) { [weak self] viDocResetState in","            switch viDocResetState {","            case let .isReseting(value):","                if value {","                    \/\/ reset in progress","                } else {","                    \/\/ reset is finished","                }","            case .failure: ","                \/\/ Error of reset viDoc","                break","            }","    }.store(in: &cancellables)"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To start the reset process, you need to perform the following method:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["peripheral.resetViDoc()"]}]}],"kind":"article","sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.vigramsdk\/documentation\/VigramSDK"]]},"metadata":{"title":"Use Reset viDoc","modules":[{"name":"VigramSDK"}],"role":"article","images":[{"identifier":"logo.png","type":"icon"}],"roleHeading":"Article"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.vigramsdk\/documentation\/VigramSDK\/UseResetVidoc","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"references":{"doc://com.vigramsdk/documentation/VigramSDK":{"type":"topic","title":"VigramSDK","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.vigramsdk\/documentation\/VigramSDK","abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/vigramsdk","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"logo.png"}]},"logo.png":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/com.vigramsdk\/logo.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"alt":"Vigram logo.","type":"image","identifier":"logo.png"}}}